%% Diagram: Spam classification pipeline
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    MSG["Incoming<br/>Message"] --> BL["Blocklist<br/>Check"]
    BL -->|Listed| SPAM["Spam<br/>Folder"]
    BL -->|Clean| AUTH["SPF/DKIM/<br/>DMARC"]
    AUTH -->|Fail| SPAM
    AUTH -->|Pass/Partial| HEUR["Heuristic<br/>Rules"]
    HEUR --> ML["Bayesian +<br/>ML Classifier"]
    ML --> DECISION{"Score<br/>&gt; 0.9?"}
    DECISION -->|Yes| SPAM
    DECISION -->|No| INBOX["Inbox"]
